comments: Holmes (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Alexander-Walker (NOP) firms up and absorbs the contact.
Alexander-Walker (NOP) makes contact to Fox's (SAC) arm at the end of his drive that affects his SQBR.  The contact occurs before he is in a shooting motion.
Holmes (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Bledsoe (NOP) firms up and absorbs the contact.
Fox (SAC) makes marginal contact to Bledsoe's (NOP) body as he starts his drive, the contact does not disrupt Bledsoe's SQBR.
Hield (SAC) cleanly blocks Adams' (NOP) layup attempt.
Barnes (SAC) grabs Adams' (NOP) arm during shooting motion, affecting his ability to finish at the rim.
Alexander-Walker (NOP) makes marginal contact to Fox's (SAC) body during his driving shot attempt.
Redick (NOP) gathers the ball and legally takes two steps before a foul is called.
Fox (SAC) makes marginal contact with Redick's (NOP) body at the end of his drive that does not affect his SQBR.
Hield (SAC) commits a take foul on Alexander-Walker (NOP).
